   <TEXT>
   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Sixty-one JESUS IS LORD Scripture: 1 Cor 12:3 There is a lord of all things Everything has its lord.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>Who is the Lord of this great universe and the things therein?</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Who is your lord?</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Neither your parents, your husband, nor your wife is your lord.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>If you think they are, who will you belong to once they die?</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>You will be a man without a lord.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>The creator of all things The universe and all creation has its creator.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>Man also has a creator.</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>The one who created all is the Lord of all.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Since all things were created by Him, all things belong to Him.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>He is the Lord of all.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>The ruler of all things There is a ruler in creation.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>There is a ruler over man and within man s heart.</S>
   <S PAR='14' RSNT='1' SNO='14'>This ruler is the Lord.</S>
   <S PAR='15' RSNT='1' SNO='15'>The redeemer of all things Man needs redemption because he has sinned.</S>
   <S PAR='16' RSNT='1' SNO='16'>The whole creation also needs redemption because it was corrupted through man s sin.</S>
   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>This is clearly seen in the Bible.</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>The redeemer of all is the Lord of all.</S>
   <S PAR='19' RSNT='1' SNO='19'>Jesus is Lord Jesus is the creator and the Lord of all.</S>
   <S PAR='20' RSNT='1' SNO='20'>Jesus is the ruler of creation; as ruler, He is the Lord of all.</S>
   <S PAR='21' RSNT='1' SNO='21'>Jesus is the redeemer of all creation; as the redeemer, He is the Lord of all.</S>
   <S PAR='22' RSNT='1' SNO='22'>How to receive Jesus as Lord Confess that you are created, ruled, and redeemed by Him.</S>
   <S PAR='23' RSNT='1' SNO='23'>Repent, confess your sins, and receive Him as your Savior.</S>
   <S PAR='24' RSNT='1' SNO='24'>Acknowledge that all that you are and have belong to Him, and that He is your Lord.</S>
   </TEXT>
